# Design Doc Routing

Design docs are modular, split by domain under `docs/design/`. See `docs/design/README.md` for the full routing table.

**Always read first:** `docs/design/core-architecture.md` (~300 lines) — shared patterns, SO system, event bus.

**Then read your domain doc.** Use only the modular docs under `docs/design/` for active work.

**Coding standards:** `.agent/skills/unity-project-conventions/SKILL.md`
